In RestEasy already provided MessageBodyReader and MessageBodyWriter.
RestEasy have JAXB conversion logic.
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Program:-Send xml and getBack xml.
--------
RequestBody:-
-----------
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<subscriber>
	<mobile>9090909090</mobile>
    <plan>199</plan>
    <amount>199</amount>
</subscriber>

http://localhost:9000/27.jax-rs_ContentHandler_without_MessageBodyReader_Writer/rest/idea/recharge

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Program:-Send JSON and getBack JSON
-------

RequestBody:-
-----------
{
  "mobile":"895988778899",
  "plan":"199-plan",
  "amount":"199"
}

content-type:-application/json

http://localhost:9000/27.jax-rs_ContentHandler_without_MessageBodyReader_Writer/rest/idea/recharge

